shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-uW","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":26334,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/13\/dua-complain-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":1918,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Whoever complains to Allah, relief will come","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is afflicted by a pressing need and complains to people, his need will never be satisfied. Whoever is afflicted by a pressing need and complains to Allah, eventually Allah will provide for him, sooner\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14455,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/30\/allah-humiliate-reject-sultan\/","url_meta":{"origin":1918,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sultan: Allah humiliates those who disrespect His authority","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever belittles the authority of Allah on the earth, Allah will belittle him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2224 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0645\u064